<plot>First loves, Eva and Jake, meet up for the first time since they were 14 years old in Paris. Eva is keen to show Jake her new found Parisienne sophistication and Jake just wants to re-discover the girl he was in love with when they were kids. As they stumble through their day together they discover cultural differences, not just with the French, but also between themselves.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?313369</url></doc>
